val PATH = "file:///Users/zacha/Desktop/Projects/TicketPrediction/"

//load the raw data
val training_df = spark.read.option("header","true").format("csv").load(PATH + "Traffic_Stops__drivers.csv").na.fill("0").na.fill(0).na.fill(0.0)

val raw_cols = Seq("ADDRESS_X","LATITUDE_X","LONGITUDE_X","AGENCY","DISPOSITION_TEXT", "EVENT_NUMBER", "INCIDENT_TYPE_DESC", "INCIDENT_TYPE_ID", "ACTIONTAKENCID","ACTIONTAKENCIDID","NEIGHBORHOOD","PRIORITY_","INSTANCE_ID","IS_JUVENILE","INTERVIEW_NUMBER","INTERVIEW_DATE", "VEHICLE_MAKE","VEHICLE_MODEL","VEHICLE_YEAR","CONTACT_TYPE_CID","LICENSE_PLATE_STATE","OFFICER_ASSIGNMENT", "REPORT_TYPE_CID","SEX","RACE","AGE","FIELD_SUBJECT_CID","AGE_RANGE_CID","BEAT")

val age_splits = Array(0.0,16.0,26.0,36.0,46.0,56.0,66.0,76.0,86.0,96.0)

// Array of all features of the model
/*val features = Array("Road","Ticketed","Time","ACURA", "ALZ", "AUDI", "BMW", "BUICK","CADILLAC", "CHEVY", "CHRYSLER", "DENA", "DODGE", "FIAT", "FORD", "SEMI", "GMC", "GEO", "HONDA", "HUMMER", "HYUNDAI", "INFINITY","ISUZU","JAGUAR","JEEP","KIA","LAND","LEXUS","LINCOLN","MAZDA","MERCURY","MERCEDES","MINI","MITSUBISHI","NISSAN","OLDSMOBILE","PLYMOUTH","PONTIAC","PORSCHE","SAAB","SATURN", "SCION","SUBARU","SUZUKI","TOYOTA","VOLKSWAGON","VOLVO","YAMAHA","OTHER_MAKE","CarYear","CarPlateState","SexVec","RaceVec")
*/

val featureCols = Array("ACURA", "ALZ", "AUDI", "BMW", "BUICK","CADILLAC", "CHEVY", "CHRYSLER", "DENA", "DODGE", "FIAT", "FORD", "SEMI", "GMC", "GEO", "HONDA", "HUMMER", "HYUNDAI", "INFINITY","ISUZU","JAGUAR","JEEP","KIA","LAND","LEXUS","LINCOLN","MAZDA","MERCURY","MERCEDES","MINI","MITSUBISHI","NISSAN","OLDSMOBILE","PLYMOUTH","PONTIAC","PORSCHE","SAAB","SATURN", "SCION","SUBARU","SUZUKI","TOYOTA","VOLKSWAGON","VOLVO","YAMAHA","OTHER_MAKE","CarYear","SexVec","RaceVec","AgeEE","CarPlateVec","RoadVec","Time")


/*
Features Data Frame Columns
#   Address (Road)
#   Action Taken Id (Citation | No Citation)
#   Date (Time) 
#   Vehicle Make 
#   Vehicle Model 
#   Vehicle Year 
#   License Plate State 
#   Sex
#   Race 
#   Age range
*/


val featureFrame = (
    training_df
        .withColumn("Ticketed", when($"ACTIONTAKENCIDID".cast("double") >= 3.0,1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("ACURA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ACCR" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ACCU" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ACUR" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ACURA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ALUR", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("ALZ", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ALZ", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("AUDI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "AUDI", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("BMW", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "BMW", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("BUICK", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "BUIC" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "BUICK", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("CADILLAC", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CADI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CADILLAC", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("CHEVY", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CGEV" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHE" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHEV" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHEVEROLET" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHEVI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHEVROLET" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHEVY" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHVY", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("CHRYSLER", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHRY" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHRYS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CHRYSLER" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "CRY" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PT", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("DENA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "DENA", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("DODGE", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "DODG" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "DODGE", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("FIAT", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "FIAT", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("FORD", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "FORD", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SEMI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "FREIGHT" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "FRHT" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MACK", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("GMC", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "GENERAL MOTORS CORP." or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "GMC", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("GEO", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "GEO", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("HONDA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HON" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HOND" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HONDA", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("HUMMER", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HUMM", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("HYUNDAI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HUYU" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYAN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYND" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYUA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYUN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYUND" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "HYUNDAI", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("INFINITY", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "INFI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "INFIN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "INFINITI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "INFINITY", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("ISUZU", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "ISUZ", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("JAGUAR", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "JAG" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "JAGU", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("JEEP", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "JEEP", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("KIA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "KIA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "KIA FORT" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "KIA MOTORS CORP.", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("LAND", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LAND", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("LEXUS", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LEXI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LEXS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LEXU" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LEXUS", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("LINCOLN", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LINC" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LINCOLN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "LINCOLN / LINCOLN-CONTINENTAL", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("MAZDA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MADZ" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MAZ" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MAZD" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MAZDA", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("MERCURY", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MECR" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MERC" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MERCURY" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MERG", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("MERCEDES", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MERCEDES" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MERZ", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("MINI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MINI", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("MITSUBISHI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MITI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MITS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MITSUBISHI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "MITZ", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("NISSAN", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "NISS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "NISSAN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "NISSIAN", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("OLDSMOBILE", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "OLDS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "OLDSMOBILE", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("PLYMOUTH", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PLYM", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("PONTIAC", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PONT" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PONTAIC" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PONTIAC", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("PORSCHE", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PORS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "PORSCHE", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SAAB", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SAAB", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SATURN", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "sATR" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SATU" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SATURN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "STRN", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SCION", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SCIO" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SCION", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SUBARU", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUB" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUBA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUBU", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("SUZUKI", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUZI" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUZK" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "SUZU", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("TOYOTA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "TOYA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "TOYO" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "TOYOTA" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "TOYT", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("VOLKSWAGON", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VOLK" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VOLKS" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VOLKSWAGEN" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VOLKSWAGEN / VOLKSWAGON" or
            $"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VW", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("VOLVO", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "VOLV", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("YAMAHA", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "YAMA", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("OTHER_MAKE", when($"VEHICLE_MAKE" === "", 1).otherwise(0))
        .withColumn("CarYear",$"VEHICLE_YEAR".cast("double"))
        .withColumn("CarPlateState",$"LICENSE_PLATE_STATE")
        .withColumn("AgeE", $"AGE".cast("double"))
        .withColumn("Road",regexp_extract($"ADDRESS_X",raw"[X]*[\s]*([A-Z0-9]+[\/A-Z0-9\s\/]*)",1))
        .withColumn("Hour", regexp_extract($"INTERVIEW_DATE",(raw"([1-9]{0,1}[\d]{1}):[\d]{2}:[\d]{2}\s[A-Z]{2}"),1))
        .withColumn("AMPM", regexp_extract($"INTERVIEW_DATE",(raw"[\d]{2}:[\d]{2}:[\d]{2}\s([A-Z]{2})"),1))
        .withColumn("Time", when($"AMPM" === "AM", $"Hour".cast("double")).otherwise($"Hour".cast("double") + 12.0))
        
        ).na.fill("_")
     
val roadIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("Road").setOutputCol("RoadIndex")
val roadEncoder = new OneHotEncoder().setInputCol("RoadIndex").setOutputCol("RoadVec")    

val plateIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("CarPlateState").setOutputCol("CarPlateIndex")
val plateEncoder = new OneHotEncoder().setInputCol("CarPlateIndex").setOutputCol("CarPlateVec")

val sexIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("SEX").setOutputCol("SexIndex")
val sexEncoder = new OneHotEncoder().setInputCol("SexIndex").setOutputCol("SexVec")

val raceIndexer = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("RACE").setOutputCol("RaceIndex")
val raceEncoder = new OneHotEncoder().setInputCol("RaceIndex").setOutputCol("RaceVec")

val age_bucketize = new Bucketizer().setInputCol("AgeE").setOutputCol("AgeEE").setSplits(age_splits)

//featureFrame.select("INTERVIEW_DATE","Time","AMPM","Hour","Road","CarPlateState").where("Road = \"\"").take(10).foreach(println)

val indexPipeline = (new Pipeline().setStages(Array(sexIndexer,raceIndexer,plateIndexer, roadIndexer,sexEncoder, raceEncoder, plateEncoder, roadEncoder, age_bucketize)))

val indexFrame = indexPipeline.fit(featureFrame).transform(featureFrame).drop("ADDRESS_X","LATITUDE_X","LONGITUDE_X","AGENCY","DISPOSITION_TEXT", "EVENT_NUMBER", "INCIDENT_TYPE_DESC", "INCIDENT_TYPE_ID", "ACTIONTAKENCID","ACTIONTAKENCIDID","NEIGHBORHOOD","PRIORITY_","INSTANCE_ID","IS_JUVENILE","INTERVIEW_NUMBER","INTERVIEW_DATE", "VEHICLE_MAKE","VEHICLE_MODEL","VEHICLE_YEAR","CONTACT_TYPE_CID","LICENSE_PLATE_STATE","OFFICER_ASSIGNMENT", "REPORT_TYPE_CID","SEX","RACE","AGE","FIELD_SUBJECT_CID","AGE_RANGE_CID","BEAT","AgeE","Hour","AMPM").na.drop

//indexFrame.show()

val assembler = new VectorAssembler().setInputCols(featureCols).setOutputCol("features")

val gbt = new RandomForestClassifier()
    .setLabelCol("Ticketed")
    .setFeaturesCol("features")
    .setNumTrees(10)
    .setRawPredictionCol("accuracy")
    .setProbabilityCol("confidence")


val featuresPipeline = (new Pipeline().setStages(Array(assembler,gbt)))

val splits = indexFrame.randomSplit(Array(0.8,0.2))

val (trainingData, testData) = (splits(0),splits(1))

val trainingFeaturesDF = featuresPipeline.fit(trainingData).transform(testData)

trainingFeaturesDF.registerTempTable("model")
